  "text": "As a metalloproteinase associated with the extracellular matrix (ECM) [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] , ADAMTS-1 cleaves aggrecan and versican [CITATION_3] , RodriguezManzaneque et al. 2002 . ADAMTS-1 also possesses anti-angiogenic activity [CITATION_4] ) and ADAMTS-1 or its C-terminal half region suppresses tumor growth and experimental metastatic potential [CITATION_5] ).",
